{"tid":1504532,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"加強勇武避彈衣，歡迎比意見改善","createTime":"2019-08-25T10:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T17:00:28.000Z","uid":259963,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a93d7570f4e39a53eb1ce69ef14c1734b343a02","tid":1504532,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"我見現場好多勇武都都只係薄薄一件黑衫就捱棍捱彈好心痛<br />\n上網見到外國有人用non-newtonian fluid(非牛頓流體)黎做避彈衣，用埋實彈黎試係有用<br />\n雖然佢係用左40-70層黎整，但佢係用金屬子彈黎試<br />\n應對黑警嘅橡膠彈可以唔需要咁多層，同埋重點係個個都整到<br />\n最簡單嘅例子係粟粉加水同埋香口膠<br />\n香口膠就容易處理，但製作成本相對高，建議做重點保護人體<br />\n粟粉加水就難d處理，但製造成本低，建議用黎做盾嘅加強，但會重左<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kK-Ob_dichQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkK-Ob_dichQ&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=2ac7468b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kK-Ob_dichQ</a><br />\n依段片最後佢係試失敗左，但我覺得係佢戇鳩射落個盒底到先會fail<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlqS60Cbark\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJlqS60Cbark&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=2ca6d823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlqS60Cbark</a><br />\n香口膠應該係為人熟悉d，可以咭穿汽水罐<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無幫助，歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b8b0a3eda8214494a0fa19ccf39f0f9b8f7ca1","tid":1504532,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1aa5bc7c42ce4757e0c903fbbe6789fc280d2f","tid":1504532,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n有無專業d嘅幫手比意見？"},{"pid":"ae404d84fbc082cc6c77ce94914137c6d7a9ce7f","tid":1504532,"uid":42414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"612721811"},{"pid":"943eb33401dacbc23cde3c55d288a594e98620d1","tid":1504532,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/grepa98.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fmilitary%2Fgrepa98.html&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=20634123\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/military/grepa98.html</a><br />\n三本書加瓷磚，特種兵教你自製防彈衣！"},{"pid":"480f3af90fe803411a476dd09d7866be1d365aee","tid":1504532,"uid":48579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"沒有武器 再多防具也是徒然"},{"pid":"44d53fa6c68a1be8d552bc784b802701a854f6ad","tid":1504532,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480f3af90fe803411a476dd09d7866be1d365aee","tid":1504532,"uid":48579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"沒有武器 再多防具也是徒然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"至少fa同物資可以加強到保護<br />\n<br />\n武器可以再諗"},{"pid":"963b7abb07ca8602afc270aa4a312130e661ec20","tid":1504532,"uid":310528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f632989ad85fe2ff0e15afc3f0826dc1025cbb","tid":1504532,"uid":42414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480f3af90fe803411a476dd09d7866be1d365aee","tid":1504532,"uid":48579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:55:52.000Z","msg":"沒有武器 再多防具也是徒然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-2